We need to show that the following three properties are forced:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\check{1}\in\dot{G}$
\end_inset

,
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{G}$
\end_inset

 is closed under binary 
\begin_inset Formula $\land$
\end_inset

,
 and
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
For every 
